<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vouch for Primo | Legitimacy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            /* Gamit ang iyong background image */
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url('https://r.jina.ai/i/9e00667a216441ca913982e0573c054e');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Glassmorphism Design */
        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 420px;
            width: 85%;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        h1 { 
            font-size: 32px; 
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        p { 
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 35px; 
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .vouch-button {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1877f2, #0056b3);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(24, 119, 242, 0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .vouch-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(24, 119, 242, 0.7);
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #166fe5, #004494);
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            opacity: 0.7;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <h1>Salamat sa Tiwala!</h1>
    <p>Para sa aking <b>transparency</b> at <b>legitimacy</b>, maaari po kayong mag-iwan ng vouch sa aking official Facebook post.</p>
    
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/v/1EJ2FKrfCP/" class="vouch-button" target="_blank">
        VOUCH HERE 
    </a>

    <div class="footer">
        Verified Transaction Wall
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
